/// Sector behavior profiles for each market scenario.
/// bull    — broad growth, tech leads, staples steady
/// bear    — broad decline, staples resilient, finance hit hard
/// sideways — flat across sectors, low vol
/// volatile — mixed (tech up, finance down, energy wild)
/// blackSwan — everything crashes, staples least damaged
/// mortgageCrisis — RE/Finance crash, Energy boost
